{"id":751,"date":"2022-04-04T17:07:00","date_gmt":"2022-04-04T14:07:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=751"},"modified":"2022-03-23T21:51:04","modified_gmt":"2022-03-23T19:51:04","slug":"easy-steps-to-changing-banks","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/easy-steps-to-changing-banks\/","title":{"rendered":"Easy Steps to Changing Banks: Making it Painless"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Many reasons can have you looking to change bank accounts. It could be better service, lower fees, digital payments, or you\u2019re seeking one with branches in more convenient locations. But are there easy steps to changing banks?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Switching banks may initially appear overwhelming and intimidating, and there are sacrifices and hard decisions to make. If you\u2019re considering other banking options and don\u2019t know how to make this leap, here\u2019s a guide to show you how to make a quick and painless switch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are multiple causes of switching bank accounts, but the process is not as simple as tapping on a button. It\u2019s an intentional decision to change banks but one that has the potential of many things going wrong. Keep reading to learn the steps to take when making a painless banking institution switch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" area-label=\"ez-toc-toggle-icon-1\"><label for=\"item-673d661cd8658\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;direction:ltr;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20p